{"tid":386151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[發動技能] 我覺得我同神嘅距離近左好多","createTime":"2017-09-03T16:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T16:06:31.000Z","uid":81277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae49bf5b0fc577d565368be82dfc1f59532351f8","tid":386151,"uid":81277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"話說今日同個朋友去屯門行街 <br />\n順便等埋兩個朋友再食dinner<br />\n我地喺starbucks坐左一陣之後打算繼續行街<br />\n然後就有3個女仔過黎叫我地2個試聽吓耳機<br />\n<br />\n佢地話係佢地人手做 想我地俾啲意見<br />\n咁我一開始以為係咩ig shop啲店主打算賣定咩<br />\n同埋反正仲有個幾鐘先食飯冇乜所謂就話okay啦<br />\n點知佢拎個試聽用嘅耳機比我用 開始播聖詩 <br />\n我就知仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後就開始sell話全部都係弟兄姊妹手工做blah blah blah<br />\n之後佢就問我地叫咩名 交換電話 add個facebook<br />\n我只係講左我個名 <br />\n我朋友就俾佢add左fb但冇accept到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後佢就拎左呢盒嘢俾我地2個 一人一盒<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/03/235859_c13a3b4458d3709f9141a24131c64d46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F03%2F235859_c13a3b4458d3709f9141a24131c64d46.jpg&h=febd7edd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後我就記得之前見過蘋果日報有報導過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我收到完全唔知俾咩反應好 <br />\n唯有禮貌講聲thank you然後拉住我朋友走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/000050_bbab22891c7f5cd1e3053a1758612662.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F000050_bbab22891c7f5cd1e3053a1758612662.jpg&h=93f6ab18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打開係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用呢個耳機聽左一首3分半鐘長嘅聖詩<br />\n仲要睇埋官網...<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/000339_2a752ed12df8eb98341dc1c3c4b98577.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F000339_2a752ed12df8eb98341dc1c3c4b98577.jpg&h=eab75c16&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/000341_b0da2876fd4f5b2a68bfc30da97b6cba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F000341_b0da2876fd4f5b2a68bfc30da97b6cba.jpg&h=d796c843&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/000343_463d8d8cf050e0653372a9c719ea90fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F000343_463d8d8cf050e0653372a9c719ea90fa.jpg&h=dfc366bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/000345_13faf42839d711460dc5e9a2d55d97a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F000345_13faf42839d711460dc5e9a2d55d97a2.jpg&h=41397580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我覺得我簡直係接觸到神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n音質就...大家應該知啦 錫安劍咁出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}